snippet.title: Sonic at the Olympic Games – Tokyo 2020™
snippet.description:
Ready? Set... GO! Sonic at the Olympic Games - Tokyo 2020 is leaping off the starting blocks for a worldwide release on May 7.
Keep yourself in the loop by pre-registering NOW: https://www.olympicvideogames.com/sonic/en/
